window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Familiar faces, new enemies, and untold danger beneath the surface.</p> <p>With the border secure, Jadyn and the griffin knights have returned to the academy to investigate the warded door leading to ancient ruins.</p> <p>But time is not a luxury they have.</p> <p>When unknown forces infiltrate the academy grounds, leaving a trail of bodies in their wake, Jadyn's squad embark on a perilous mission to track the assailants and ensure that the ruin's mysteries don't fall into the wrong hands.</p> <p>Can the Griffin Knights of Atania rise to another challenge and protect all that they hold dear as they try to unlock the secrets of ancient magicâ€¦</p>"; 
